2017年'''巴爾米拉攻勢'''是[[敘利亞|敘利亞]]政府軍於2017年1月13日在[[霍姆斯省|霍姆斯省]]東部發起的軍事行動，意圖收復於2016年12月被[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]][[巴爾米拉之戰_(2016年12月)|攻佔]]的古城[[巴尔米拉|巴尔米拉]]。

[[File:SyrianDesert1.svg|thumb]]

2017年2月4日，敘政府軍收復哈揚（Hayyan）天然氣田。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-liberates-hayyan-gas-fields-west-palmyra/|title=Syrian Army liberates Hayyan Gas Fields in west Palmyra|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=2017-02-04|publisher=Al-Masdar News|accessdate=2017-06-25|archive-date=2017-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170520222103/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-liberates-hayyan-gas-fields-west-palmyra/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2月7日，伊斯蘭國奪回哈揚氣田。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/isis-retakes-hayyan-gas-fields-new-bid-expand-west-palmyra/|title=ISIS retakes Hayyan Gas Fields in new bid to expand west of Palmyra|date=2017-02-07|publisher=Al-Masdar News|accessdate=2017-06-25|archive-date=2017-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170517125919/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/isis-retakes-hayyan-gas-fields-new-bid-expand-west-palmyra/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2月14日，敘政府軍再次收復哈揚氣田。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/2017-02/15/c_1120469887.htm |title=叙利亚政府军收复一座重要天然气田 |publisher=新華網 |date=2017-02-15 |accessdate=2017-06-25 |archive-date=2017-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170711212544/http://news.xinhuanet.com/2017-02/15/c_1120469887.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>2月16日，伊斯蘭國又奪回哈揚氣田部分氣井。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-enters-jihar-gas-fields-fierce-battle-isis-west-palmyra/|title=Syrian Army enters Jihar Gas Fields after fierce battle with ISIS in west Palmyra|last=Fadel|first=Leith|date=2017-02-16|work=AMN - Al-Masdar News|accessdate=2017-02-16|language=en|archive-date=2020-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925054129/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-enters-jihar-gas-fields-fierce-battle-isis-west-palmyra/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2月18日，敘政府軍再次控制整個哈揚氣田。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-advances-within-15km-palmyra-liberating-new-area/|title=Syrian Army advances within 15km of Palmyra after liberating new area|last=Fadel|first=Leith|work=Al-Masdar News|date=2017-02-18|accessdate=2017-02-20|archive-date=2019-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190204063641/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-advances-within-15km-palmyra-liberating-new-area/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

敘政府軍到2017年2月27日已進抵[[巴尔米拉|巴尔米拉]]城外數公里處。<ref name=xh20170228>{{Cite news |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2017-02/28/c_1120539617.htm |title=叙利亚政府军逼近古城巴尔米拉 |publisher=新華網 |date=2017-02-28 |accessdate=2017-03-01 |archive-date=2017-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170302131752/http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2017-02/28/c_1120539617.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>3月1日，敘軍收復位於巴爾米拉城以西的巴爾米拉古堡。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/2017-03/02/c_1120553230.htm |title=叙利亚政府军收复巴尔米拉古堡 |publisher=新華網 |date=2017-03-02 |accessdate=2017-03-02 |archive-date=2017-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170302113528/http://news.xinhuanet.com/2017-03/02/c_1120553230.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>3月2日，敘政府軍宣佈再次收復古城巴尔米拉。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://ca.reuters.com/article/topNews/idCAKBN1691GI |title=Syrian army announces recapture of Palmyra from Islamic State |publisher=Reuters |date=2017-03-02 |accessdate=2017-03-04 |archive-date=2019-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190502004654/https://ca.reuters.com/article/topNews/idCAKBN1691GI |dead-url=no }}</ref>3月3日，敘政府軍收復在東面市郊的巴爾米拉機場。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://sputniknews.com/middleeast/201703031051232663-syrian-army-daesh-pamyra-airport/ |title=Get Out! Syrian Army Erases Daesh From Palmyra Airport |publisher=Sputnik |date=2017-03-03 |accessdate=2017-03-05 |archive-date=2019-05-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190507022757/https://sputniknews.com/middleeast/201703031051232663-syrian-army-daesh-pamyra-airport/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

